Imports: terra, jpeg, plyr, StableEstim, Rcpp (>= 1.0.9)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
SystemRequirements: GDAL (>= 2.2.3), GEOS (>= 3.4.0), PROJ (>= 4.9.3),
        sqlite3
